featured_reviews.review_id: Situated in  Old Jhargram its the most popular and old Masjid in Jhargram. Recently after some maintenance and extension work its looks awesome. Timely prayer maintained throughout the year. During the festival EID it becomes very crowded. The pond in front of it should be cleaned and the approach road towards it from main road is very narrow for overcrowded events.
